resource/2028_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Los Angeles 2028\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2028_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2028_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It was disappointing it was decided that it would not be in LA, particularly before we even had a chance to show it,\\\" said Australian B-Girl Rachel \\\"Raygun\\\" Gunn.\", \"from\": 891, \"to\": 1054, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1015, \"end\": 1025, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\", \"score\": 0.9988256452112488, \"rank\": 0.0009618914628928631, \"text\": \"Australian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I think that was possibly a little premature.\", \"from\": 1056, \"to\": 1102, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I wonder if they are kicking themselves now.\\\"\", \"from\": 1103, \"to\": 1148, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Organisers ensured breaking made the most of its time in the spotlight in Paris, pumping up the volume for an excited crowd that included rapper Snoop Dogg.\", \"from\": 1150, \"to\": 1306, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1224, \"end\": 1229, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.999999999996362, \"rank\": 3.657236239580531e-12, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 1295, \"end\": 1305, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Snoop_Dogg\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Snoop Dogg\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Snoop_Dogg\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Snoop_Dogg\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I still do not believe that I am here because breaking is so different,\\\" said Italian 